        tag: "What if",
        title: "What if every notification was a tax?",
        body: "Each ping is a small auction the chapter would refuse to enter. The state in chapter 3 doesn't suppress citizens; it refuses to <em>amplify</em> the signals that cause them to fight each other. Your phone is a tiny totalitarian state in this respect. Mute one app per week for six weeks. Note which crimes (against your own attention) stop happening."
      ,
        title_th: "ถ้าทุก notification เป็นภาษี?",
