        title: "Subtract one thing",
        body: "Right now, before you scroll. Identify one thing in your day that you could simply not do tomorrow — not delegate, not optimise, not. The chapter's claim is that you will think of three excuses before you finish reading this sentence. The exercise is to ignore all three.",
